name: ANGRY APES by AA Int'l ft. "Bored to Death" by THR33LL

metadata.name: Angry Ape #1
metadata.description: We're utilizing our IP from the Bored Ape Yacht Club to bring you the original music track 'Bored to Death' by THR33LL together with a 4444 unique collection of Angry Apes PFP with enhanced imagery at 4000 x 4000 pixels. Your Angry Apes NFT is a provable token on the Ethereum blockchain that serves as your lifetime membership to AA International and grants you access to members-only benefits. This is only the beginning.
